description: 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom condo is located in the heart of Germantown, one of Nashville's most vibrant and desirable neighborhoods! This 4th floor condo offers 1000sf of thoughtfully designed living space, filled with natural light! It features hardwood floors, stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and a convenient in-unit washer & dryer. There is also additional storage on the same floor, and a covered & gated assigned parking space. The location is truly unbeatable — you'll be within easy walking distance of First Tennessee Park, Nissan Stadium, the Bicentennial Mall, the Farmers Market, and Brooklyn Bowl, as well as some of the city's most celebrated restaurants and nightlife. With Broadway and all things downtown Nashville just minutes away, this condo places you right in the middle of everything Music City has to offer! Call listing agent today for your a private showing!
